      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "地名。秦地，位于今陕西省临潼县东北。",
      "examples": [
        "蕞，地名。在秦，一曰在新丰。——《集韵》"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "蕞"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "adjective",
      "meaning": "小的，微小的。",
      "examples": [
